displayName: Tavern: Fierce Tiger of the Azure Horn

You haven't been to the main guild in the city of
Rein Garnet, have you? First, please go there and
talk to the guild leader.

And if you don't join the guild, you won't be able
to take on quests or do anything else at this
branch guild.

Welcome, magical girls. This is the Traveling
Guild. How may I assist you?

If you have any questions or concerns, feel free
to ask.

The leader of this golden city is a loli monster
named Sphinx, and her name is \C[2]Faris\C[0]. She
can be a bit nervous, but she is generally a kind
person who cares about the people.

It seems to be a custom here for the receptionist
to suddenly ask visitors riddles.

It seems that the visiting magical girls are being
troubled by the magical beasts that periodically
appear in the Gritia Graveyard, so they are being
asked for requests each time.

If you haven't had an audience yet, it would be a
good idea to visit Lady Faris.
